ame": "Saki and the Crucible of Debauchery", "steam_appid": 2652500, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "controller_support": "full", "detailed_description": "<h1>💟Add in WishList!!💟</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2652500/extras/7cc4ed07fcd3861a4a8075d062dcfe92.poster.avif?t=1750385840\" width=616 height=600 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2652500/extras/7cc4ed07fcd3861a4a8075d062dcfe92.webm?t=1750385840\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2652500/extras/7cc4ed07fcd3861a4a8075d062dcfe92.mp4?t=1750385840\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Falter in battle, and this shrine maiden won't stay pure for long...</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><strong>Game Progression</strong></u></h2><br>A dungeon crawl necessitates preparation. Give Saki the best equipment available and prepare her for whatever may come her way.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2652500/extras/3acf0f2f7bc5c40b33bf29da60507697.avif?t=1750385840\" width=616 height=462 /></span><br><br>In her crawl through the dungeon, Saki will do battle with abonimations who will go after her body to seize victory.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2652500/extras/5927d61b6e77499e3f94c9b176d3d4dc.avif?t=1750385840\" width=616 height=462 /></span><br><br>But it's not just demons Saki has to deal with. She must also navigate her way through devious traps.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2652500/extras/7704ff906a85a804387f7